      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUMMER DREAM (2) was well fancied last time over 365m at Nowra but in traffic and fell. Can find winning form this time. BUSY MAN (1) is a well performed sprinter ideally suited at the shorter trips. Was in the money last time (18.29) over 320m at this track in a Free For All. Form at the trip excellent including 14 wins. Has a strong record from this draw, notching two wins and two minor placings from four starts. Overdue and is among the main hopes. INFAMOUS STATHAM (8) was well off top last time, finishing 5th (19.52) in a NG at Bulli. Form here at this distance is strong including four wins. Has a strong record from box 8, including two wins. Better than last start and can bounce back. STEPHEN WITHERAP (7) is a last start winner and can go on with it.",
